<paragraph id="8FB22F030A533B37C8ADC2E888EDD6E5" pageId="1" pageNumber="88">
<taxonomicName id="D5EF03F7B2EF5D9E4ED25D8FECE70AE4" authority="Semenov, 1927" authorityName="Semenov" authorityYear="1927" class="Insecta" family="Carabidae" genus="Parololius" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Parololius" order="Coleoptera" pageId="1" pageNumber="88" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">Parololius</taxonomicName>
Semenov, 1927: 232 [unjustified emendation of 
